{"tid":2140570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新系統垃圾隔濾率跌八成","createTime":"2020-08-05T05:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T06:23:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4024b32241a30e3d346e86c090016167c3448339","tid":2140570,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/YEQJ44YIS2AP3ZMQNL4OZKAGFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FYEQJ44YIS2AP3ZMQNL4OZKAGFU%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeas2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=ec98c4e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FYEQJ44YIS2AP3ZMQNL4OZKAGFU%2F&h=35a28a92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/YEQJ44YIS2AP3ZMQNL4OZKAGFU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新系統垃圾隔濾率跌八成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/51RpRqM2M0J3Cw1ZfN6SHYqzR8A=/190x115/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PKHYQ3P5A7PYFS4K67LEVNLZ4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F51RpRqM2M0J3Cw1ZfN6SHYqzR8A%3D%2F190x115%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPKHYQ3P5A7PYFS4K67LEVNLZ4M.jpg&h=9ed473db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新圍污水處理廠由潘樂陶旗下安樂工程承建，現已局部營運。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】新圍污水處理廠懷疑污水溢流外，新系統隔濾垃圾比率亦偏低。據渠務署，現有系統每一萬立方米污水則可過濾308.7公斤垃圾；新系統測試每處理一萬立方米污水，僅過濾出54.9公斤垃圾，過濾率勁跌八成。不願具名投訴人質疑廠房隔濾系統故障，憂垃圾隨污水排出大海。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：安樂排污滿瀉傳惡臭  泵回管道直出白海豚棲息地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渠務署否認機械故障<br />\n<br />\n渠務署資料顯示，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n渠務署否認隔濾機械故障，。。。。。。。。。。。。署方指新建設施整體表現需待日後全面運作才可確定。<br />\n<br />\n教大科學與環境學系副教授曾耀輝分析，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Wg7c0VAz8ZeSf3lJScQsyF3RzTc=/666x280/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5O5DXWWEVVHPMHBSSBGL3WPYCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWg7c0VAz8ZeSf3lJScQsyF3RzTc%3D%2F666x280%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5O5DXWWEVVHPMHBSSBGL3WPYCI.jpg&h=3b7881cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2606430bfc022e47ea913c084039972e859288de","tid":2140570,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"中國系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf5d9d0c8a56daa21e5325ae405a727054fa5db","tid":2140570,"uid":35438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbad333b662cab94a59321e1cc19d5b0a328c4b","tid":2140570,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"安樂工程集團，簡稱安樂工程或ATAL，創立於1977年。公司主席為香港工程師學會前會長潘樂陶，是現任香港律政司司長鄭若驊的丈夫。公司主要業務為屋宇裝備工程及環境裝備工程，曾參與港珠澳大橋香港段過境設施工程。據上市文件披露，大約2成收益來自政府部門。"},{"pid":"b4e6ba24c3cb9914b35d0af3624f2aeae4f0eb93","tid":2140570,"uid":118031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"無故障 本身就係咁廢"},{"pid":"876aebceb95df7d7c9f505913449deb143a9a4cf","tid":2140570,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"爭咁撚遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c020a349ef8db4e7e74dd3e5fa48403f13156383","tid":2140570,"uid":349976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾嘅垃圾系統？"},{"pid":"ff65bdc15e0ae8a029bf17a3eae4126796233a95","tid":2140570,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4024b32241a30e3d346e86c09001